   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Making a focus for children in Argentina</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this Project is to promote the development of language and pre-literacy throughout early childhood before enter to the school. By working with children for several years we have discovered that many problems related with mathematics and other subjects come from problems not properly solved in Reading comprehension in early childhood. A group of professionals work with aproximately 200 children by dividing them in groups according to their age in 5 different locations.</narrative>
  </description>
